@startuml
title ATTENDANCE.RF001 - Registrar Presença

actor TEACHER

boundary Frontend
control AttendanceResolver
control AttendanceService
control FrequencyService
control NotificationService
control AuditService

database PostgreSQL

TEACHER -> Frontend : Seleciona turma + data

Frontend -> AttendanceResolver : mutation registerAttendance()

AttendanceResolver -> AttendanceService : register(dto)

AttendanceService -> PostgreSQL : validarProfessorTurma()

PostgreSQL --> AttendanceService : resultado

alt Professor autorizado

    AttendanceService -> AttendanceService : validarData()

    alt Data válida

        loop Para cada aluno

            AttendanceService -> PostgreSQL : verificarDuplicidade()

            alt Registro inexistente

                AttendanceService -> PostgreSQL : salvarPresença()

            else Registro duplicado

                AttendanceService --> AttendanceResolver : erro duplicidade

            end

        end

        AttendanceService -> FrequencyService : recalcularFrequencia()

        FrequencyService -> PostgreSQL : buscarRegistros()

        PostgreSQL --> FrequencyService : presenças

        FrequencyService -> FrequencyService : calcularPercentual()

        FrequencyService -> PostgreSQL : atualizarHistorico()

        alt Frequência < 75%

            FrequencyService -> NotificationService : enviarAlerta()

            NotificationService -> PostgreSQL : buscarEmails()

            NotificationService --> FrequencyService : alerta enviado

        end

        AttendanceService -> AuditService : registrarOperacao()

        AuditService --> AttendanceService : log salvo

        AttendanceService --> AttendanceResolver : sucesso

        AttendanceResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 201

        Frontend --> TEACHER : Presença registrada

    else Data futura

        AttendanceResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 400

        Frontend --> TEACHER : Data inválida

    end

else Professor sem vínculo

    AttendanceResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 403

    Frontend --> TEACHER : Sem permissão

end

@enduml